1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

The main target image shows a structure composed of 10 blocks arranged in two layers.  The structure resembles a small archway. The first layer has two central, vertically-oriented, cylindrical blocks (yellow) supported by two shorter, rectangular blocks in front and behind them.  The second layer has a roof-like structure, with a triangular block (orange) on top, supporting an arch-shaped block (red) which in turn is supported by two square blocks (blue).  The structure also contains a separate triangular block (orange/red) located at the bottom-right.
